* Run on the PostgreSQL server (the following instructions assume EL 6.x - 7.x with PostgreSQL RPM 9.5 - 9.6):

sudo yum install dialog openssl expect

sudo su postgres

cd postgresqlca

ca_template/bin/edit_vars

./install.sh

Follow the on screen instructions for editing $PGDATA/pg_hba.conf

In PostgreSQL 9.x, restart the server.  In PostgreSQL 10 and above, reload.
